sequenceDiagram
  participant UI as React UI (Mic PCM 16k)
  participant API as ResourceLibrary.API (WS)
  participant CQ as MediatR Stream
  participant SVC as AiAudioService
  participant SC as Score Service (WS)

  UI->>API: GET /api/aiAudio/score/live (WS)
  API-->>UI: WS upgraded
  UI->>API: binary PCM frames (16k, s16le)
  API->>CQ: ScoreSingingLiveQuery(pcm stream)
  CQ->>SVC: ScoreSingingLiveAsync(pcm stream)
  SVC->>SC: WS connect + PCM
  SC-->>SVC: JSON { score, partial_text }
  SVC-->>CQ: SingingLiveUpdate
  CQ-->>API: IAsyncEnumerable<update>
  API-->>UI: WS text frames {InstantScore, PartialText}
